sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant VLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over S3,HF: Flow 2 - Model Initialization (startup)
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        S3->>HF: KServe init downloads model files<br/>S3 API / AWS credentials
        Note right of HF: Model loaded into<br/>GPU/CPU memory
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1 - Built-in Content Detection
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Note right of BuiltIn: Regex PII scan<br/>File-type validation<br/>Custom detector execution
        BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: ContentsAnalysisResponse<br/>[detections with type, score, span]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,HF: Flow 2 - HuggingFace Content Detection
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Note right of HF: PyTorch model inference<br/>AutoModelForSeqClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM
        HF-->>Orchestrator: ContentsAnalysisResponse<br/>[detections with label, score]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,VLLM: Flow 3 - LLM Judge Content Detection
    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Judge->>VLLM: OpenAI-compatible chat completion<br/>HTTP plaintext (cluster-internal)
        VLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response
        Judge-->>Orchestrator: ContentsAnalysisResponse<br/>[detections with metric, score]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,VLLM: Flow 3 alt - LLM Judge Generation Evaluation
    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
        Judge->>VLLM: Evaluate prompt+response pair<br/>HTTP plaintext
        VLLM-->>Judge: LLM judge verdict
        Judge-->>Orchestrator: Generation evaluation result
    end
